{"data":[{"date":"15:02 15/06","title":"Ch\u00e2n d\u00e0i Nga \"ve v\u00e3n\" quanh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u00f3ng qu\u00e2n","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/15/chan-dai-nga-ve-van-quanh-khach-san-tuyen-anh-dong-quan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1edd The Sun cho hay, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao \u0110T Anh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">&ldquo;Chuy\u1ec7n \u1ea5y&rdquo; \u1edf World Cup l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m l\u1edbn, r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n s\u1ebd ra &ldquo;lu\u1eadt&rdquo; th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. X\u01b0a nay, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Nam M\u1ef9 v\u1ed1n tho\u00e1ng trong vi\u1ec7c cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 v\u1ee3 v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i trong th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra gi\u1ea3i, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n kh\u1eaft khe h\u01a1n.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh b\u1ecb g\u00e1i Nga ve v\u00e3n, quy\u1ebfn r\u0169, t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh b\u1ecb g\u00e1i Nga ve v\u00e3n, quy\u1ebfn r\u0169, t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/dT-Anh-tha-cua-chuyen-ay-World-Cup-Chan-dai-dt-anh5-1529034466-815-width660height450.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110T Anh lu\u00f4n tho\u00e1ng khi d\u1ef1 c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i l\u1edbn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi ri\u00eang \u0110T Anh, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 &ldquo;truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng&rdquo; cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ee3 v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i \u0111i theo, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 c\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn. N\u0103m nay kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7. HLV Gareth Southgate cho d\u00e0n WAGs Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u1ebfn Nga c\u1ed5 v\u0169, \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7, ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf chung kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3ng qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh khi t\u1edbi tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 4 sao ForRestMix \u1edf ngo\u1ea1i \u00f4 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 St Petersburg, Nga. N\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ea5p n\u1eadp nh\u01b0ng theo t\u1edd The Sun, con g\u00e1i \u1edf th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 St Petersburg r\u1ea5t xinh \u0111\u1eb9p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy\u1ec3n Anh qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Premier League. V\u00ec th\u1ebf nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb9p \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c s\u1ed1ng g\u1ea7n kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Harry Kane v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Theo \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng h\u1eb9n h\u00f2 Tinder, m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t ch\u00e2n d\u00e0i h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u00ednh 10km c\u1ee7a n\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3ng qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"1\" title=\"1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/dT-Anh-tha-cua-chuyen-ay-World-Cup-Chan-dai-dt-anh2-1529034511-501-width660height719.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Zhanna, 26 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u1ea7y quy\u1ebfn r\u0169</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"1\" title=\"1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/dT-Anh-tha-cua-chuyen-ay-World-Cup-Chan-dai-dt-anh1-1529034466-334-width660height625.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u00f4 g\u00e1i t\u00f3c v\u00e0ng xinh \u0111\u1eb9p Alexis, 21 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n &quot;t\u00e2m s\u1ef1&quot; v\u00e0 &quot;l\u00e0m b\u1ea1n&quot; v\u1edbi sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f4 g\u00e1i t\u00f3c v\u00e0ng 21 tu\u1ed5i Alexis chia s\u1ebb \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm &quot;m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi World Cup k\u1ebft th\u00fac&quot;. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb9p 26 tu\u1ed5i Zhanna khoe \u1ea3nh th\u01b0\u1edbt tha v\u1edbi v\u00e1y tr\u1eafng v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i th\u00f4ng tin c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n tr\u00ean \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng Tinder. Nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n d\u00e0i \u0111ang ra s\u1ee9c &ldquo;th\u1ea3 th\u00ednh&rdquo; d\u00e0n sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 HLV Southgate c\u00f3 c\u1ea5m s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng h\u1eb9n h\u00f2 tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn v\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh hay kh\u00f4ng. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u00ec c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ea1i s\u1ee9c h\u00fat l\u1edbn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng c\u00f4 g\u00e1i St Petersburg c\u1ef1c k\u00ec xinh \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 quy\u1ebfn r\u0169.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng \u0103n ch\u01a1i, ngay c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i th\u1eadm ch\u00ed y\u00ean b\u1ec1 gia th\u1ea5t v\u1ee3 con \u0111\u1ec1 hu\u1ec1. Vi\u1ec7c HLV Southgate kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea5m xxx c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o h\u1ec7 l\u1ee5y x\u1ea5u cho \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng H\u1ee3p (TTVN)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3636","checkdouble":"188554"},{"date":"16:54 15/06","title":"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n, HAGL g\u00f3p 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/u19-viet-nam-cong-bo-danh-sach-sang-trung-quoc-tap-huan-hagl-gop-5-cai-ten.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch 25 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n nh\u1eb1m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 v\u00e0 U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m. </h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian mi\u1ec7t m\u00e0i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n PVF, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch, HAGL g\u00f3p 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch, HAGL g\u00f3p 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/AZ4A9834.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n b\u1ed5 \u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng V-League v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t th\u00ec trong chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i n\u00e0y, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 mang theo 25 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ra nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 v\u00e0 U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m.\u00a0</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 \u00fd th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 trong su\u1ed1t giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u1eeba qua.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u01b0a t\u1eadp h\u1ee3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t do m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u01b0\u1edbng l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 h\u1ea1ng Nh\u00ec QG nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n t\u1eebng c\u00f9ng \u0110T U20 VN tham d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup 2017 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh quan \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u01b0 duy ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u\u00a0 th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00f4m nay, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 10 ng\u00e0y t\u1eeb 16/6 \u0111\u1ebfn 25/6 t\u1edbi. Tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t b\u1ea1n, \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u 3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y 17/6, 20/6 v\u00e0 23/6 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande (B) v\u00e0 CLB Meizhou Meixian Techand FC \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Trung Qu\u1ed1c. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 1/7 t\u1edbi 14/7 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Danh sach U19 Viet Nam\" title=\"Danh s\u00e1ch U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/DS-U19-tap-huan-TQ.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Danh s\u00e1ch U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vck-u19-chau-a-2018-co-hoi-nao-cho-u19-viet-nam-168-186585.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/18/vck-u19-chau-a-2018-co-hoi-nao-cho-u19-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vck-u19-chau-a-2018-co-hoi-nao-cho-u19-viet-nam-168-186585.html\">VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nL\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 t\u1ea1i Jarkata, Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn ch\u00e2u \u00c1 l\u00e0 U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, U19 \u00dac. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-trieu-tap-31-cau-thu-u19-viet-nam-de-mo-ve-world-cup-168-186380.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/20/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-trieu-tap-31-cau-thu-u19-viet-nam-de-mo-ve-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-trieu-tap-31-cau-thu-u19-viet-nam-de-mo-ve-world-cup-168-186380.html\">HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp 31 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 m\u01a1 v\u00e9 World Cup</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eb1m t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n k\u1ef3 t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup 2 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp 31 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam cho \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3635","checkdouble":"188565"},{"date":"17:30 15/06","title":"Sao HAGL s\u1eafp ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng v\u00ec l\u1ed7i \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/15/sao-hagl-sap-phai-nhan-an-phat-nang-vi-loi-danh-nguoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a HAGL c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t ngu\u1ed9i t\u1eeb ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF sau h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 13 V-League 2018.</h2><h2>Sao HAGL s\u1eafp ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng v\u00ec l\u1ed7i \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh HAGL s\u1eafp ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh HAGL s\u1eafp ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/a_hoang_zing.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Trung v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa HAGL vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 13 V-League 2018, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a HAGL c\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u khi c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Douglas b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Douglas sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng kh\u00e1 gay g\u1eaft tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 l\u1ebd tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n Qu\u1ed1c H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng r\u00fat th\u1ebb cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng t\u1eeb d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, VFF \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c. Theo tin t\u1eeb ban \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh V-League 2018 cho bi\u1ebft chi\u1ec1u nay 15/6 s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn b\u0103ng h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 xem x\u00e9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng va ch\u1ea1m c\u1ee7a V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 Rosa Taudin Douglas. N\u1ebfu x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi phi th\u1ec3 thao, Ban \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh s\u1ebd l\u00e0m h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c g\u1eedi sang Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh cho r\u1eb1ng l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang xem x\u00e9t l\u1ea1i pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i t\u1eeb ph\u00eda BTC, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 d\u00e0nh cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u1ecb n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb: \u201cN\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sai, Ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ebd x\u1eed l\u00fd. CLB kh\u00f4ng bao che\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i V-League nh\u01b0 Omar hay Oseni \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t ngu\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng khi \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e0 n\u0103ng V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 b\u1edfi h\u00e0nh vi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3634","checkdouble":"188571"},{"date":"15:52 15/06","title":"Liverpool v\u00e0 Chelsea chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Porto","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/arsenal-va-chelsea-chi-35-trieu-bang-mua-hau-ve-porto.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Telles c\u1ee7a Porto, Liverpool c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea v\u00e0 Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Telles</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Vi\u1ec7c Marcos Alonso \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real v\u00e0 Barca theo \u0111u\u1ed5i l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Telles c\u1ee7a Porto thay Marcos Alonso h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Telles c\u1ee7a Porto thay Marcos Alonso h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Chelsea-muon-mua-Alex-Telles-cua-Porto-thay-Marcos-Alonso-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Alex Telles</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThe Blues nh\u1eafm Alex Sandro c\u1ee7a Juventus nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Theo Mirror, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-phuong-an-b-vu-sandro-172-163178.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Telles</span> c\u1ee7a Porto \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992. The Kop mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Andrew Robertson. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Alberto Moreno \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Porto.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAlex Sandro \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t B\u0110N m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. Ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh ghi 3 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 13 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 B\u0110N. V\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ed1t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Porto \u0111\u00f2i 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Telles v\u1edbi Porto c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Telles r\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Porto chi ban Alex Telles voi gia 35 trieu bang\" title=\"Porto ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Alex Telles v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/arsenal-va-chelsea-chi-35-trieu-bang-mua-hau-ve-porto.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Porto ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Alex Telles v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, song Chelsea hay Liverpool v\u1eabn s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, song b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi Porto.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3633","checkdouble":"188556"},{"date":"16:18 15/06","title":"NHM Arsenal nh\u1eafn HLV Unai Emery: H\u00e3y ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c mua Golovin","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/15/nhm-arsenal-nhan-hlv-unai-emery-hay-ngay-lap-tuc-mua-golovin.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsenal mua Aleksandr Golovin, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o NHM Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal t\u1eebng h\u1ecfi mua Golovin v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNga \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 5-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018, v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0, h\u1ecd \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong hai t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"NHM mu\u1ed1n Arsenal mua Aleksandr Golovin h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"NHM mu\u1ed1n Arsenal mua Aleksandr Golovin h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/nhm-arsenal-nhan-hlv-unai-emery-hay-ngay-lap-tuc-mua-golovin.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal t\u1eebng h\u1ecfi mua Golovin v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aleksandr Golovin l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0110T Nga, anh g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 3/5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Golovin khi\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn th\u1ed5n th\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i, v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd chi ra \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb CSKA Moscow kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 v\u1eabn quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-chi-15-trieu-bang-mua-sao-tuyen-nga-172-187521.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Golovin</span>, Juventus c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Song Arsenal v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>NHM mu\u1ed1n Arsenal mua Golovin</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal mua Aleksandr Golovin, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o NHM Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho khen ngoi Golovin\" title=\"Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i Golovin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Nga-vs-Saudi-Arabia-bang-A-World-Cup-2018-Tuyet-voi-Golovin-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>NHM mu\u1ed1n Arsenal mua Golovin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i twitter, \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o NHM \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London k\u00eau g\u1ecdi HLV Emery \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Emirates.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Neil b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nga, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, Arsenal h\u00e3y k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Golovin\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Ariel Ehsan Reynaldi cho r\u1eb1ng: \u201cGolovin r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Arsenal m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNick Name Ahmad Gozali Siahaan kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cGolovin r\u1ea5t gi\u1ecfi \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng, Arsenal n\u00ean k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nIsmail Mostafa: \u201cArsenal h\u00e3y h\u1ecfi mua Golovin tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus\u201d</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nStar Lord: \u201cGolovin s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Rosicky ti\u1ebfp theo t\u1ea1i Arsenal\u201d</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSILVERSURFER: \u201cN\u1ebfu Wilshere ra \u0111i, Golovin s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3632","checkdouble":"188557"},{"date":"11:48 15/06","title":"B\u1ea1n th\u00e2n l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Ronaldo bu\u1ed3n b\u1ef1c","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/15/ban-than-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-ronaldo-buon-buc.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nuno Gomes - nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Real.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\"C\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ecb ru\u1ed3ng b\u1ecf\" l\u00e0 c\u1ee5m t\u1eeb Nuno Gomes d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 mi\u00eau t\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha kh\u00e1t khao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p cho CLB, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch Barcelona l\u00e0m v\u1edbi Xavi, Iniesta hay Lionel Messi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 Ronaldo s\u1ebd ra \u0111i nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn anh \u1ea5y \u0111ang bu\u1ed3n b\u1ef1c. BL\u0110 Real \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd d\u00e0nh cho CR7 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e1ng tr\u00f4i qua, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n v\u1eabn v\u1eady\", Nuno Gomes cho bi\u1ebft.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ea1n th\u00e2n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do Ronaldo bu\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u1ea1n th\u00e2n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do Ronaldo bu\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/1_1.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i l\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb Real Madrid.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Ronaldo l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh nh\u01b0ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5p so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p. Anh \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n Real c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch Barcelona t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Lionel Messi\", c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThu nh\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Ronaldo hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/n\u0103m, thu\u1ed9c h\u00e0ng top th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn k\u00e9m xa so v\u1edbi Neymar (32 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/n\u0103m) v\u00e0 Lionel Messi (40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/n\u0103m). BL\u0110 Real t\u1eebng h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cho Ronaldo nh\u01b0ng sau n\u00e0y, th\u1ee9 CR7 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u00e2u n\u00f3i c\u1ee5t l\u1ee7n \"gi\u1edd ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong 13 n\u0103m \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t Barcelona, Messi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BL\u0110 \u01b0u \u00e1i t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 8 l\u1ea7n. G\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2021 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Nou Camp, thu nh\u1eadp c\u1ee7a \"El Pulga\" \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i t\u1eeb 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00ean 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3631","checkdouble":"188545"},{"date":"11:09 15/06","title":"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n MU s\u1ebd c\u00e0i c\u1eafm khi b\u00e1n Martial","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/tiet-lo-dieu-khoan-mu-se-cai-cam-khi-ban-martial.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man United s\u1ebd c\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean mua l\u1ea1i Martial trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u1ecfi Old Trafford h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>MU t\u00ednh b\u00e1n Martial</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n MU s\u1ebd c\u00e0i c\u1eafm khi b\u00e1n Martial h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n MU s\u1ebd c\u00e0i c\u1eafm khi b\u00e1n Martial h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/13/tiet-lo-dieu-khoan-mu-se-cai-cam-khi-ban-martial.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU s\u1ebd b\u00e1n Martial h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Lamboley x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Martial \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay \u201cNh\u00e0 h\u00e1t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1\u201d h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u00d4ng cho r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Alexis Sanchez \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00f4ng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn Martial m\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 sa s\u00fat.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t 18 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Premier League m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua. V\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 Martial \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tham d\u1ef1 World Cup c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Martial v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a HLV Mourinho \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Man United c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 Martial ra \u0111i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Mourinho s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Martial mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. V\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eafng nghe nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i.</div>\r\n<h2>Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00e0i c\u1eafm th\u00eam c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Metro \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng Man United s\u1ebd c\u00e0i th\u00eam \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea7n tr\u0103m ti\u1ec1n ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1ebfu c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c b\u00e1n Martial sau \u0111\u00f3. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Martial mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Man United lo ng\u1ea1i r\u1eb1ng Martial c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c. V\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf d\u0129 nhi\u00ean s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb 22 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ng\u1eb7t ngh\u00e8o.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Ed Woodward l\u00ean n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n n\u0103m 2013, Man United th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00ednh k\u00e8m nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n v\u00e0o trong c\u00e1c h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n h\u01b0\u1edfng 25% ti\u1ec1n ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau n\u00e0y v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u00e1n Michael Keane cho Burnley n\u0103m 2015. Man United c\u0169ng c\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua l\u1ea1i khi b\u00e1n Depay cho Lyon v\u00e0o n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU kh\u00e1c:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-se-de-martial-roi-mu-voi-mot-dieu-kien-172-188464.html\">Mourinho s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 Martial r\u1eddi MU v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-vu-sao-khung-psg-172-188458.html\">MU nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c m\u1eebng v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng PSG</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3630","checkdouble":"188540"},{"date":"11:26 15/06","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u1ecfi mua Chris Smalling","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/23/day-doi-bong-dau-tien-hoi-mua-chris-smalling.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>West Ham mu\u1ed1n mua Chris Smalling c\u1ee7a MU, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Metro \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 28 tu\u1ed5i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">West Ham h\u1ecfi mua Smalling</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Pellegrini \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n West Ham thay David Moyes, c\u1ef1u HLV Man City \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"West Ham mu\u1ed1n mua Chris Smalling \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"West Ham mu\u1ed1n mua Chris Smalling \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/23/day-doi-bong-dau-tien-hoi-mua-chris-smalling.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>West Ham mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Smalling\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nWest Ham mu\u1ed1n mua Chris Smalling c\u1ee7a MU, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Metro \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 28 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Smalling l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a M.U. L\u00fd do l\u00e0 b\u1edfi Phil Jones v\u00e0 Eric Bailly th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f2n Victor Lindelof h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp r\u1ea5t ch\u1eadm.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Smalling ch\u1ec9 \u1edf m\u1ee9c tr\u00f2n vai, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f2n m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua. T\u1eeb khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn M.U, ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec5n m\u1ed7i k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Smalling l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Old Trafford.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Smalling n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 Smalling ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o M.U, song Mourinho v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Smalling cho West Ham n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Smalling toa sang mang ve 3 diem cho Quy do\" title=\"Smalling t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng mang v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/smalling2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Smalling n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i trung v\u1ec7 \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Mourinho, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 Clement Lenglet c\u1ee7a Sevilla. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n nh\u01b0 Varane hay Toby Alderweireld c\u0169ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, M.U s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Smalling.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i West Ham th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-chot-gia-ban-smalling-cho-arsenal-172-180397.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Smalling</span>, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn gi\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n di\u1ec5n ra quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Smalling kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3629","checkdouble":"188542"},{"date":"09:25 15/06","title":"Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n David Luiz cho Arsenal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/5/chelsea-tu-choi-ban-david-luiz-voi-gia-17-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsenal mua David Luiz nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, Chelsea v\u1eeba t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal h\u1ecfi mua David Luiz</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 David Luiz g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u cho Chelsea. M\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi HLV Conte khi\u1ebfn anh b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a The Blues, sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal mua David Luiz v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsenal mua David Luiz v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/30/Arsenal-mua-David-Luiz-voi-gia-17-trieu-bang-nhung-bi-tu-choi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 David Luiz&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e2u thu\u1eabn gi\u1eefa Luiz v\u00e0 Conte v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p The Blues sa th\u1ea3i Conte, Luiz m\u1edbi ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00fac n\u00e0y Conte v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb v\u00e0 Luiz \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi d\u00e0nh cho m\u00ecnh. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/monaco-muon-mua-david-luiz-172-185268.html\" target=\"_blank\">Monaco quan t\u00e2m David Luiz</span>, Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Laurent Koscielny d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng c\u00f2n Chambers hay Holding kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, Luiz s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea. \u00d4ng Unai Emery \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Luiz, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Emirates.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n David Luiz cho Arsenal</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal mua David Luiz nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, Chelsea v\u1eeba t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n David Luiz cho Arsenal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n David Luiz cho Arsenal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/6/Chelsea-tu-choi-ban-David-Luiz-cho-Arsenal-voi-gia-17-trieu-bang-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Luiz cho Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThe Blues kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, h\u1ecd \u01b0u ti\u00ean gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Theo Le10Sport, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987, Chelsea s\u1ebd \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 David Luiz c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i bi\u00ean gi\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Luiz v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 \u00edt h\u01a1n 28 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 31 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, con s\u1ed1 28 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t cao David Luiz s\u1ebd&nbsp;ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3628","checkdouble":"188530"},{"date":"10:06 15/06","title":"Mario Gotze s\u1eafp c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/8/25/Trung-ve-David-Luiz-va-nhung-vu-tro-lai-lich-su-hinh-anh-17.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mario Gotze t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, theo Mirror, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mario Gotze mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Dortmund</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mario Gotze t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Dortmund, song s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng t\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Bayern Munich.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mario Gotze t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh Arsenal hay Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mario Gotze t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh Arsenal hay Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/16/Mario-Gotze-toi-Ngoai-hang-Anh-Arsenal-hay-Liverpool-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mario Gotze mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Dortmund</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d, Gotze ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Dortmund. Khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Ruhr, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 b\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a Gotze cho Dortmund l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00fac n\u00e0y, ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nh\u01b0ng anh b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Dortmund, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Gotze mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mario Gotze t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, theo Mirror, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mario Gotze va ngay tro lai\" title=\"Mario Gotze v\u00e0 ng\u00e0y tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/8/25/Trung-ve-David-Luiz-va-nhung-vu-tro-lai-lich-su-hinh-anh-17.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mario Gotze mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/sao-dortmund-tha-thinh-liverpool-172-188137.html\" target=\"_blank\">Gotze mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng Klopp \u1edf Liverpool</span>. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c mang c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1edbi Anfield l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Liverpool s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m Mario Gotze. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea7m trung \u1edf Premier League nh\u01b0 Everton, West Ham, Leicester v\u00e0 Newcastle \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Gotze. Song ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3627","checkdouble":"188531"},{"date":"09:57 15/06","title":"N\u00d3NG: M.U c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 3 trong h\u00e8 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/15/mu-gia-han-hop-dong-thanh-cong-voi-thu-thanh-dean-henderson.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CLB Man United v\u1eeba ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi sao tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U21 Anh Dean Henderson, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Dean Henderson l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong danh s\u00e1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U h\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><br>\r\n            <img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 3 trong h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 3 trong h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/mu-gia-han-hop-dong-thanh-cong-voi-thu-thanh-dean-henderson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>M.U ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Dean Henderson t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2020</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CLB Man United \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 ba trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y sau Fred v\u00e0 Diogo Dalot. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh Dean Henderson.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 21 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a M.U m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Shrewsbury theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y anh \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3i PFA League One c\u1ee7a n\u0103m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a anh t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn BL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng n\u00e0y t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2020, k\u00e8m th\u00eam \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gia h\u1ea1n k\u00e8m theo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi k\u00eanh MUTV sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn, Henderson vui v\u1ebb cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;T\u00f4i th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Shrewsbury theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, sau \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n cho b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi d\u00e0nh cho t\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i n\u1eefa. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 nh\u01b0ng nay \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m sau m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba qua, tuy nhi\u00ean M.U v\u1eabn l\u00e0 CLB l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 d\u0129 nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tin-nong-world-cup-2018-ngay-156-4-tuyen-thu-bdn-that-nghiep-truoc-dai-chien-mo-man-421-188523.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/tin-nong-world-cup-2018-ngay-156-4-tuyen-thu-bdn-that-nghiep-truoc-dai-chien-mo-man.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tin-nong-world-cup-2018-ngay-156-4-tuyen-thu-bdn-that-nghiep-truoc-dai-chien-mo-man-421-188523.html\">Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y 15/6: Sao MU s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh</span><br>\r\nC\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (15/6). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u1eebng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p>Minh Long (TTVN)</o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3626","checkdouble":"188533"},{"date":"07:21 15/06","title":"V\u1ee3 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Nga \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0 \"ti\u00ean n\u1eef gi\u00e1ng tr\u1ea7n\"","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/15/vo-tuyen-thu-nga-dep-nhu-tien-nu-giang-tran.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tuy kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 trong l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nga, nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Dmitri Tarasov l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p ghen t\u1ef5 khi c\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb9p Anastasia Kostenko. </h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ee3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tarasov tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Nga xinh \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0 ti\u00ean n\u1eef h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ee3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tarasov tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Nga xinh \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0 ti\u00ean n\u1eef h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Hinh-anh-vo-tien-ve-Tarasov-tuyen-thu-Nga-xinh-dep-nhu-tien-nu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">N\u0103m 20 tu\u1ed5i, Anastasia Kostenko g\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa \u00fd khi \u0111\u1ea1t danh hi\u1ec7u \u00c1 h\u1eadu 2 Hoa h\u1eadu Nga 2014. Sau \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f4 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u theo \u0111u\u1ed5i nghi\u1ec7p th\u1eddi trang v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p kinh doanh.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hoi thang 1 nam nay, Kostenko ket hon voi tien ve Dmitri Tarasov sau mot thoi gian hen ho. Co khong it lan duoc cac to tap chi noi tieng bau chon la nang WAGs (vo va ban gai cau thu) dep nhat xu so bach duong. Trong anh: Khoanh khac tinh tu cua cap d\" title=\"H\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m nay, Kostenko k\u1ebft h\u00f4n v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Dmitri Tarasov sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian h\u1eb9n h\u00f2. C\u00f4 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c t\u1edd t\u1ea1p ch\u00ed n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea7u ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 n\u00e0ng WAGs (v\u1ee3 v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7) \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u1edf b\u1ea1ch d\u01b0\u01a1ng. Trong \u1ea3nh: Kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc t\u00ecnh t\u1ee9 c\u1ee7a c\u1eb7p \u0111\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Ba-xa-tuyen-thu-Nga-dep-tua-tien-nu-giang-tran-wag-2-1528959414-984-width660height437.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">H\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m nay, Kostenko k\u1ebft h\u00f4n v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Dmitri Tarasov sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian h\u1eb9n h\u00f2. C\u00f4 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c t\u1edd t\u1ea1p ch\u00ed n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea7u ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 n\u00e0ng WAGs (v\u1ee3 v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7) \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u1edf b\u1ea1ch d\u01b0\u01a1ng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tien ve Dmitri Tarasov hien dang khoac ao CLB Lokomotiv Moscow. O World Cup 2018 dien ra tren que nha, tien ve 31 tuoi duoc HLV Stanislav Cherchesov goi vao DT Nga du ngay hoi bong da lon nhat hanh tinh nay. Anastasia Kostenko la niem tu hao cua chan\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Dmitri Tarasov hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB Lokomotiv Moscow. \u1ede World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean qu\u00ea nh\u00e0, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 31 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Stanislav Cherchesov g\u1ecdi v\u00e0o \u0110T Nga d\u1ef1 ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh n\u00e0y. Anastasia Kostenko l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o c\u1ee7a ch\u00e0n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Ba-xa-tuyen-thu-Nga-dep-tua-tien-nu-giang-tran-wag-3-1528959414-151-width660height440.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Dmitri Tarasov hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB Lokomotiv Moscow. \u1ede World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean qu\u00ea nh\u00e0, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 31 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Stanislav Cherchesov g\u1ecdi v\u00e0o \u0110T Nga d\u1ef1 ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh n\u00e0y. </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kostenko tung dat danh hieu A hau 2 Hoa hau Nga 2014.\" title=\"Kostenko t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ea1t danh hi\u1ec7u \u00c1 h\u1eadu 2 Hoa h\u1eadu Nga 2014.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Ba-xa-tuyen-thu-Nga-dep-tua-tien-nu-giang-tran-wag-4-1528959414-378-width660height882.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">V\u1ee3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tarasov t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ea1t danh hi\u1ec7u \u00c1 h\u1eadu 2 Hoa h\u1eadu Nga 2014.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhan sac cua my nhan 24 tuoi nay khien khong it phai dep phai ganh ty.\" title=\"Nhan s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a m\u1ef9 nh\u00e2n 24 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ph\u00e1i \u0111\u1eb9p ph\u1ea3i ganh t\u1ef5.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Ba-xa-tuyen-thu-Nga-dep-tua-tien-nu-giang-tran-wag-6-1528959414-231-width660height434.jpg\"></t