ckdouble":"188519"},{"date":"20:25 14/06","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 14/6: M.U nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c m\u1eebng t\u1eeb Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/19/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-146-mu-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-tu-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 14/6.\r\n</h2><h2>M.U nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c m\u1eebng t\u1eeb Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u1edd b\u00e1o qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson Becker \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gia nh\u1eadp Los Blancos v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70-80 tri\u1ec7u euro. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a, M.U kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai David De Gea &ndash; m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng n\u0103m c\u1ee7a K\u1ec1n K\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 146 MU nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c m\u1eebng t\u1eeb Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 146 MU nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c m\u1eebng t\u1eeb Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/23/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-146-MU-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-tu-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 14/6: Real chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Salah \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">heo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp Hector Cuper, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mohamed Salah &ldquo;g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 100% k\u1ecbp ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Uruguay&rdquo;. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c nhanh h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng cho \u0110T v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Ai C\u1eadp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ee5 Martial</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ph\u00e1p x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chia tay Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1ef1 tin gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n t\u1ef1 gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Martial.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Premier League \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c FA c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Unai Emery s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n 2 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t trong 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Man City v\u00e0 Chelsea. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ea1i cho t\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, khi Arsenal \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o Top 4 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Unai Emery trinh bay ro viec tan dung nhung cai ten san co.\" title=\"HLV Unai Emery tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y r\u00f5 vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1eb5n c\u00f3.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/25/unai-emery-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Man City v\u00e0 Chelsea ngay 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nH\u00f4m nay, Lopetegui ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;N\u1ed7i h\u1ed5 th\u1eb9n&rdquo; c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha &ndash; HLV Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft &ldquo;s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn&rdquo; v\u1edbi K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n sa th\u1ea3i sau khi \u0111i \u0111\u00eam v\u1edbi Los Blancos, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 ng\u00e0y l\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3624","checkdouble":"188496"}]}